So however you live and whatever you’ve lived through, and whoever you are and wherever you want to be in life, treatment at Paracelsus Recovery’s exclusive rehab facilities will help you see clearly not only how far you’ve come, but where you can go next.

What we treat

The first step at Paracelsus Recovery is the last one you'll take alone.

Whoever you are, whatever you’ve lived through, our bespoke treatment programmes are here to help you heal. We have decades of experience helping ultra-wealthy clients, with the privacy, exclusivity, and personalised care you are accustomed to.

At Paracelsus Recovery’s exclusive rehab facility, we specialise in providing compassionate, tailored support for any and all mental health conditions. Our programmes will address every underlying cause of your pain, from the physical and cellular to the psychological and neurobiological. Recovery is a journey, but we will guide you every step of the way.  

Learn About Mental Health Treatment

Whether you’re battling substance abuse, behavioural addictions, or a reliance on prescription medications, we can help. Our interdisciplinary approach addresses the root causes of dependency, including emotional pain and stress, and provides you with tools for a fear-free, balanced life.

Explore Addiction Treatment

At Paracelsus Recovery, we treat eating disorders as the complex and multifaceted conditions they are. All of our treatment programmes go beyond your relationship with food, as we recognise that it is only the tip of the iceberg. Instead, by addressing the crux of the issue, such as trauma, anxiety, or perfectionism, we empower you to reshape your relationship with food.

Discover Eating Disorder Recovery

Our chronic conditions programs target cellular health and genetic factors to restore your body’s natural balance, reduce inflammation, and boost your energy levels. Together, we can help you overcome the challenges your chronic condition has brought to your life.

View Chronic Condition Support

How we treat

A unique approach, focused on mind, body and soul, one client at a time

One-size-fits-all isn’t conducive to healing, but our unique approach, tailor-made for every single one of our patients, is.  We are the only treatment centre in the world to offer a minimum of 15 dedicated professionals to every patient. So, throughout your stay, you will be guided by a team of world-renowned doctors, therapists and specialists.

With our combination of cutting-edge medical excellence and holistic approaches to well-being, we are the only treatment centre in the world to truly address the full spectrum of your health.

A sanctuary of safety and compassion

Wherever you are on your journey, whatever challenges you face, and whoever you are, we are here for you. With absolute discretion, we provide the care you need in a secure, confidential, and nurturing environment.

A dedicated team

A team of 15 leading experts is fully committed to your well-being. From your personal psychiatrist and attending physician to your live-in therapist and dedicated client coordination team, we stand by your side 24/7.

Private and exclusive

A private, exclusive, and entirely discreet experience—designed to prioritize and protect you.
